            "details": {
              "(a) Projection model + circle equation [15]": "12/15 — Correctly derives perspective projection for image plane Z=f and shows a circle on plane Z=Z0 projects to a circle, with correct (x_c,y_c,r) expressions for that convention. However, the requested model/sign convention was specifically (x,y,-f) with x=-fX/Z, y=-fY/Z; the report switches conventions and does not explicitly reconcile the sign difference.",
